{"tid":1197632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中央物資問題","createTime":"2019-06-10T04:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T06:03:10.000Z","uid":9131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"51f87806fe7d0286056b3fc6b3051b25790bf24f","tid":1197632,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"69各位義士其中一個唔夠狗鬥既原因係裝備問題<br />\n<br />\n一個口罩擋到既始終有限<br />\n而不停好有心買補給品既後緩未必完全知道實際情況需要啲咩 <br />\n可能變到飲品過份充足 護目鏡一個都冇<br />\n<br />\n好想知道點樣可以有效率咁提供到物資俾佢地<br />\n保護大家既安全同士氣<br />\n<br />\n大家有眼睇唔同組織既表現<br />\n相信方法唔會係捐錢俾眾志同民陣<br />\n<br />\n有冇一個透明度高少少 <br />\n至少俾人知啲錢會用去邊既方法<br />\n<br />\n係出力之餘 可以盡綿力出埋錢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理無用 勇武有理</span></span>"},{"pid":"dc6c7c7bd3792b743554f0603d6c1365c4ff1c6d","tid":1197632,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5802a4b1e3b20d379e97910e1ae724fc5cf95484","tid":1197632,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cbc4cb3204224b168764035ef9f23950544f446","tid":1197632,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:07:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce2866e5091221e7a81ce7f2aa25ed7883fc83c7","tid":1197632,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b42ce4b5a081461061ffec329a1f9da267b3ac23","tid":1197632,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c722145ea836a0